topic: Movie Workflow Series ("Tv series explorative search")

goals.1: Return the number of seasons and episodes per season of the tv series
goals.2: Get the number of episodes in which the cast members played a role. Who are the most present actors?
goals.3: Check who is the actor who acted in more films while working on "How I met your mother" and who is the actor who participated in more films after the end of the tv series.
goals.4: Compare HIMYM with the tv series "The Office (US)" in terms of number of seasons, episods and cast members.
goals.5: Return how many of the actors who are members of the cast of the tv series have [Kavin Bacon number](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Six_Degrees_of_Kevin_Bacon#:~:text=Kevin%20Bacon%20himself%20has%20a,Bacon%20number%20is%20N%2B1.) equal to 2
